{"tid":477222,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"[抵贊] 半年學識普通話  三星 Bixby 大陸推出","createTime":"2017-11-22T23:15:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-23T12:19:36.000Z","uid":17103,"like":0,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f2292c0cabf58ad7e88e78df5e52d8463efe62d0","tid":477222,"uid":17103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T23:15:26.000Z","msg":"半年學識普通話  三星 Bixby 大陸推出 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4523/209571/1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.eprice.com.hk%2Fmobile%2Ftalk%2F4523%2F209571%2F1%2F&d=zs9%2FH5MOh%2By9Cb8WNyr33YzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=19cb3425\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4523/209571/1/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.techinasia.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/Samsung-Pay-in-China.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.techinasia.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F03%2FSamsung-Pay-in-China.jpg&h=98f402d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n版主虎仔有喜歡玩手機嘅朋友，玩厭 Galaxy S8 再換埋 Galaxy Note 8，暫時改為「寵幸」 iPhone X，但依然未有機會用廣東話同 Samsung 智能助理 Bixby 溝通，因為 Bixby 推出時只懂得英語和韓語，<span style=\"color: pink;\">廣東話市場咁細，就自然不在研發的首位。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.theandroidsoul.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/bixby-china.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theandroidsoul.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F11%2Fbixby-china.jpg&h=c57ac99b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n半年學識普通話  三星 Bixby 大陸推出<br />\n<br />\n不過鄰近強國就唔同，<span style=\"color: red;\">有 13 億人口同龐大的消費力，Samsung 自然要落足心機冧大陸客</span>。昨日 Samsung 就在北京舉行 Bixby 中國發佈會，宣佈 Bixby 今個月底正式登陸，不過<span style=\"color: red;\">香港蝗語 (打擊低能仔重編) </span>用戶毋須太過興奮，因為支援的只有 Galaxy S8、S8+、Note 8 的大陸國行版，還有下月上市的「土豪機」心繫天下 W2018 摺機，只要更新軟件就可以正式使用 Bixby。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.sammobile.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/samsung-bixby-in-china-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sammobile.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F11%2Fsamsung-bixby-in-china-1.jpg&h=1eded82c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSamsung 還特別為大陸市場推出<span style=\"color: red;\">專屬的 Bixby 中國版 Logo</span>，又會在稍後上映的《星球大戰：最後的絕地武士》進行宣傳。跟歐美和韓國一樣，Bixby 在大陸亦會支持語音溝通，用戶只要用把口落指令，Bixby 就可以進行翻譯、掃描物品進行識別、叫車、發送社交媒體更新等功能。Samsung 亦表明明年 Bixby 2.0 會支持更多智能識別功能，亦會加入更多物聯網的元素。"},{"pid":"96ce9da5aec0e121b29feb7fd8520ed35b690185","tid":477222,"uid":17103,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T23:18:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">廣東話市場咁細，就自然不在研發的首位。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.next.nextmedia.com/images/next-photos/NextMag/1177/640pixfolder/N3_1177_022_08d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.next.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fnext-photos%2FNextMag%2F1177%2F640pixfolder%2FN3_1177_022_08d.jpg&h=25e259b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/1379222557.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2013%2F09%2F1379222557.jpg&h=f8a1da78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/1575000/1575769/IMG_0312_1024.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1575000%2F1575769%2FIMG_0312_1024.PNG&h=f9df20b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/1790000/1791835/20170421_siriwhatsapp_02_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1790000%2F1791835%2F20170421_siriwhatsapp_02_600.jpg&h=a03e5d71&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d4f534d2cadf0c9e2c448fef1bb2b9508161b089","tid":477222,"uid":5846,"like":0,"dislike":18,"score":-18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T01:52:43.000Z","msg":"不過鄰近強國就唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n乜撚野鄰近？香港係中國入面架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35323ac3d9165984bdd83e0cb7486bf0a7430ed5","tid":477222,"uid":3773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T03:31:01.000Z","msg":"關我撚事"},{"pid":"c65e16a2be2472e5993bff06342e749612cbecef","tid":477222,"uid":1557,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T03:48:36.000Z","msg":"乜siri一出就有廣東話喇咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"335955bbb21dcb11473e22cc8be1f4662c762adf","tid":477222,"uid":5846,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T03:55:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不過鄰近強國就唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n乜撚野鄰近？香港係中國入面架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講事實糾正都負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 正垃圾"},{"pid":"966f0ce55208b4cbac52d990e80cb1f4af8175c4","tid":477222,"uid":17103,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T04:24:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>乜siri一出就有廣東話喇咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無錯, 一出唔支援廣東話, 但係人地再進化就會包廣東話同國語一齊囉<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://chinese.engadget.com/2012/06/11/siri-update-support-cantonese-mandarin/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchinese.engadget.com%2F2012%2F06%2F11%2Fsiri-update-support-cantonese-mandarin%2F&d=zs9%2FH5MOh%2By9Cb8WNyr33YzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=30cb0609\" target=\"_blank\">https://chinese.engadget.com/2012/06/11/siri-update-support-cantonese-mandarin/</a><br />\n<br />\n在正在舉行的 WWDC 上，有關 iOS 6 的其中一個重點就是 Siri 的功能加強，不過在云云的功能中，我們最驚喜的，是 Siri 居然把中華地區的語言都學起來了 -- 不論是廣東話（中國大陸及香港）、普通話還是國語，大家都可以輕鬆的和 Siri 構通 ，此外 Siri 也加入了本地搜尋，這些配合其他如開啟 apps 之類同屬這次新加入 Siri 的功能，相信會讓其實用性大增，也會讓我們有更多使用 Siri 的機會；何況最新一代的 iPad 也將可以使用 Siri 呢。說著說著，我們已經開始想動口說了！大家對這個更新又有甚麼感想，不妨留言告訴我們啊！<br />\n<br />\n不如開下盤要等多幾耐先有 Google Assistant 或者 Bixby 講廣東話? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bec2ce4dbbe357d156a5d95f413cd8484c0c616c","tid":477222,"uid":12628,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T05:15:51.000Z","msg":"三叔：蓋樂世，覆蓋全世界快樂的事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0194d1b17743f92af32c2eead394a6942e7bcf2","tid":477222,"uid":1557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T05:37:56.000Z","msg":"屌你真係咩都可以用嚟打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab949a5c0bdcf0d91c09b7631ef34fc591a4b0f9","tid":477222,"uid":1518,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T05:44:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不過鄰近強國就唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n乜撚野鄰近？香港係中國入面架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n死返支那啦5毛"},{"pid":"83e8ccd071244b86097a4c9ff4e1fb